name: Dimension Gate 5.0
description:
I got thinking about interdimensional travel and out of body experiences and decided I should do a small series of Dimensional Gates. Where these gates lead to no one knows.

Are you ready for the ride?

I am.... let's go!

Dimension Gate 5.0 is a thank you gift for those who collected all four still images, Dimension Gate 1.0 - 4.0 on my main H=N account.

Ten (10) minted, any remaining will be 4 tez.

Digital sketch reworked via VQGAN+CLIP. MP4 loop with audio, 30 seconds, 23 MB. By @dehiscenceart, 2021
